text: "River" is a 2023 song by Miley Cyrus. It is the second single from her eighth studio album Endless Summer Vacation. It went to the top 30 in Australia, New Zealand, Austria, Latvia, Ireland, Lithuania, the United Kingdom, Greece, Hungary, Portugal, Poland, Norway, Panama, Croatia, Latvia, North Macedonia, Switzerland and Denmark. ==References== Category:2023 songs Category:Miley Cyrus songs Category:Dance-pop songs Category:Synth-pop songs
title: River (Miley Cyrus song)
